    <item>
      <title>特朗普媒体估值飙升，因赌徒押注大选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/trump-media-gets-a-sky-high-valuation-as-bettors-play-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 的媒体初创公司让投资者经历了一段疯狂的旅程，该公司的市值从 5 月份的高点到 9 月份的低点缩水了 70 多亿美元，然后又在不到一个月的时间内重新获得了近 30 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/trump-media-gets-a-sky-high-valuation-as-bettors-play-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 17:45:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>ASML 股价暴跌，订单量未预示芯片制造商陷入困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/asml-orders-miss-as-chip-industry-weakness-weighs-on-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿斯麦控股公司 (ASML Holding NV) 的订单仅为分析师预期的一半左右，导致其股价出现 26 年来的最大跌幅，对于这家半导体行业的领头羊来说，这是一个令人震惊的增长放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/asml-orders-miss-as-chip-industry-weakness-weighs-on-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 15:05:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
